decks.notes: The main idea of this deck is to control the board and the game through a combination of powerful spells and versatile creatures, leveraging the strengths of Kyodai, Soul of Kamigawa as the Commander. The deck includes a variety of removal spells, counter spells, card draw, and versatile threats to disrupt the opponent's game plan while setting up its own win condition. With a strong mana base and a mix of powerful planeswalkers like Teferi, Time Raveler and Jace, the Mind Sculptor, as well as efficient creatures like Tarmogoyf and True-Name Nemesis, the deck aims to outvalue and outmaneuver the opponent, ultimately gaining control of the game and securing a victory.
